00:18:50,140 --> 00:18:51,870
He fed him,

294
00:18:51,950 --> 00:18:53,070
taught him to walk,

295
00:18:53,070 --> 00:18:54,380
taught him to speak,

296
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:56,180
sent him to nursery school
in the morning,

297
00:18:56,180 --> 00:18:57,950
and coaxed him to sleep at night.

298
00:18:58,180 --> 00:19:00,260
He plays the role of a dad and a mom.

299
00:19:00,830 --> 00:19:02,630
At the same time, he worried

300
00:19:02,830 --> 00:19:05,020
that his tumor would relapse.

301
00:19:05,540 --> 00:19:07,070
Do you think it's easy for him

302
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:08,350
for the past six years?

303
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:10,420
Mr. Ning, please calm down.

304
00:19:10,420 --> 00:19:11,900
How can he calm down?

305
00:19:12,110 --> 00:19:12,870
His grandpa has been taking care of him

306
00:19:12,870 --> 00:19:13,500
despite many years

307
00:19:13,500 --> 00:19:14,350
of hardship.

308
00:19:14,350 --> 00:19:15,660
Why should we

309
00:19:15,950 --> 00:19:16,780
let her take the kid away?

310
00:19:19,950 --> 00:19:20,630
Please take a seat first.

311
00:19:20,630 --> 00:19:21,630
I have an idea.

312
00:19:21,830 --> 00:19:22,590
Sit down.

313
00:19:25,110 --> 00:19:25,710
How about this?

314
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:27,110
You can marry

315
00:19:27,870 --> 00:19:29,140
Zhiqian now.

316
00:19:29,630 --> 00:19:30,710
Then Ning Xiang

317
00:19:30,710 --> 00:19:32,540
will have a legal mom.

318
00:19:32,660 --> 00:19:33,750
If the three of you

319
00:19:33,750 --> 00:19:35,710
spend time together every day,

320
00:19:35,900 --> 00:19:36,750
he'll stop thinking

321
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:37,900
about his biological mom.

322
00:19:38,470 --> 00:19:39,260
Mr. Ning,

323
00:19:39,260 --> 00:19:40,590
what kind of idea is this?

324
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:41,900
Even if I can pretend to be one,

325
00:19:41,900 --> 00:19:43,630
I'm still not his birth mother.

326
00:19:45,500 --> 00:19:46,110
But...

327
00:19:47,420 --> 00:19:48,300
I'm not buying it.

328
00:19:54,110 --> 00:19:54,900
Ning Xiang.

329
00:19:59,070 --> 00:19:59,900
Ning Xiang,

330
00:20:01,630 --> 00:20:02,900
I want to ask you something.

331
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:04,230
Do you want

332
00:20:04,230 --> 00:20:06,070
to go with your birth mother

333
00:20:06,140 --> 00:20:06,780
or

334
00:20:07,230 --> 00:20:09,500
stay here with your dad?

335
00:20:10,020 --> 00:20:13,300
I want to be with my birth mom.

336
00:20:15,780 --> 00:20:16,710
What?

337
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:20,950
I want to be with my birth mom.

338
00:20:28,110 --> 00:20:28,780
Ning Xiang,

339
00:20:28,990 --> 00:20:29,590
come here.

340
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:34,260
Tell me.

341
00:20:34,590 --> 00:20:35,660
Do you really want to go with her?

342
00:20:36,950 --> 00:20:37,710
Ning Xiang.

343
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:40,230
If you really go with her,

344
00:20:40,230 --> 00:20:41,350
what about your dad?

345
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:44,180
She's my birth mom.

346
00:20:44,350 --> 00:20:47,350
She didn't mean to abandon me.

347
00:20:49,110 --> 00:20:49,870
Come, Ning Xiang.

348
00:20:51,590 --> 00:20:52,900
What if I don't let you go with her?

349
00:20:54,070 --> 00:20:54,870
What if I don't

350
00:20:54,870 --> 00:20:55,470
let you go with her?

351
00:20:55,470 --> 00:20:56,380
Just let me go

352
00:20:56,380 --> 00:20:58,900
with my birth mom.

353
00:20:58,900 --> 00:21:00,110
What birth mother?

354
00:21:00,110 --> 00:21:00,630
Are you sure

355
00:21:00,630 --> 00:21:01,470
she's your birth mother?

356
00:21:01,780 --> 00:21:02,710
Just let me go

357
00:21:02,710 --> 00:21:05,420
with my birth mother.

358
00:21:05,420 --> 00:21:06,180
You're not going anywhere.

359
00:21:06,180 --> 00:21:06,950
Do you hear me?

360
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:11,900
Just let me go

361
00:21:11,900 --> 00:21:14,230
with my birth mom.

362
00:21:14,230 --> 00:21:15,710
You're not going anywhere!

363
00:21:22,350 --> 00:21:23,070
Stop crying.

364
00:22:04,180 --> 00:22:05,380
I'm coming in.

365
00:22:16,710 --> 00:22:18,110
Where did he hide?

366
00:22:22,750 --> 00:22:23,950
I found you.

367
00:22:24,630 --> 00:22:27,070
Let me take a look at this little kitty.

368
00:22:31,590 --> 00:22:32,710
I made some noodles.

369
00:22:32,710 --> 00:22:34,110
Do you want some?

370
00:22:36,500 --> 00:22:37,350
Do you want some?

371
00:22:44,830 --> 00:22:45,830
Then can you come out

372
00:22:46,070 --> 00:22:47,830
and talk to me for a bit?

373
00:22:50,870 --> 00:22:51,950
Don't you like me anymore?

374
00:22:53,380 --> 00:22:54,660
I still do.

375
00:22:56,630 --> 00:22:57,230
Come here.

376
00:23:10,950 --> 00:23:12,180
Can you tell me

377
00:23:12,540 --> 00:23:13,140
why you want to go

378
00:23:13,140 --> 00:23:14,540
with your birth mother?

379
00:23:16,070 --> 00:23:18,470
Because she's my mom.

380
00:23:19,300 --> 00:23:20,660
Just for this reason?

381
00:23:21,990 --> 00:23:24,020
Since I was young,

382
00:23:24,020 --> 00:23:26,070
I always wondered
what my mom looked like

383
00:23:26,070 --> 00:23:28,950
and if she had a nice voice.

384
00:23:30,990 --> 00:23:32,350
I also wonder

385
00:23:32,350 --> 00:23:34,750
how she would praise me if I did well.

386
00:23:35,020 --> 00:23:37,710
Then you appeared in my life.

387
00:23:37,750 --> 00:23:39,590
I was so happy.

388
00:23:40,780 --> 00:23:43,630
You may visit me all the time

389
00:23:43,630 --> 00:23:45,420
and be nice to me.

390
00:23:45,420 --> 00:23:46,140
But

391
00:23:46,950 --> 00:23:50,140
I always felt something different

392
00:23:50,140 --> 00:23:51,540
compared to other mothers.

393
00:23:53,230 --> 00:23:55,020
It was until my birth mom came

394
00:23:55,020 --> 00:23:57,420
to the kindergarten to see me.

395
00:24:00,020 --> 00:24:03,350
She never talks to me when she comes.

396
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:05,590
She would watch me from afar.

397
00:24:05,710 --> 00:24:08,140
She would cry and smile now and then.

398
00:24:08,990 --> 00:24:10,070
I really want

399
00:24:10,070 --> 00:24:12,750
to be with my birth mom.

400
00:24:15,260 --> 00:24:16,590
But if you go with her,

401
00:24:17,140 --> 00:24:18,950
your dad will feel sad.

402
00:24:19,420 --> 00:24:20,630
If I leave,

403
00:24:20,630 --> 00:24:23,260
Dad will still be the same.

404
00:24:23,260 --> 00:24:25,300
But mom will be heartbroken

405
00:24:25,300 --> 00:24:27,300
without me.

406
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:29,350
How do you know

407
00:24:29,350 --> 00:24:31,110
if your dad won't be heartbroken?

408
00:24:31,710 --> 00:24:33,500
Because Dad says

409
00:24:33,500 --> 00:24:35,590
a real man

410
00:24:35,630 --> 00:24:38,590
shouldn't weep and sob all day.

411
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:43,380
He doesn't cry at all.

412
00:24:43,380 --> 00:24:45,540
Why would he feel sad?

413
00:24:49,830 --> 00:24:50,350
Mom,

414
00:24:50,350 --> 00:24:52,950
please talk to Dad

415
00:24:52,950 --> 00:24:55,830
and let me go with my birth mom.

416
00:25:05,470 --> 00:25:08,380
Why don't you come with me?

417
00:25:28,070 --> 00:25:29,350
I'm really thankful

418
00:25:29,750 --> 00:25:31,140
that you've raised Ning Xiang

419
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:33,470
so well

420
00:25:33,780 --> 00:25:34,660
all this time.

421
00:25:35,260 --> 00:25:35,990
Next time,

422
00:25:35,990 --> 00:25:36,830
just take good care

423
00:25:36,830 --> 00:25:37,900
of Ning Xiang.

424
00:25:39,630 --> 00:25:40,590
I will.

425
00:25:41,350 --> 00:25:42,420
Dr. Ning did question me

426
00:25:42,420 --> 00:25:44,380
at the coffeehouse before.

427
00:25:44,900 --> 00:25:45,990
He wanted me

428
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:47,540
to give him a definite answer.

429
00:25:48,630 --> 00:25:49,950
No matter what happens,

430
00:25:50,630 --> 00:25:52,230
I'll definitely prioritize Ning Xiang.

431
00:25:53,070 --> 00:25:54,180
My son

432
00:25:54,830 --> 00:25:55,660
is like that.

433
00:25:55,950 --> 00:25:56,780
He has a kind heart.

434
00:25:56,780 --> 00:25:57,180
But

435
00:25:57,180 --> 00:25:58,780
he's harsh with his words.

436
00:25:58,900 --> 00:26:00,110
So don't take it to heart.

437
00:26:00,470 --> 00:26:01,300
I'll make sure

438
00:26:01,300 --> 00:26:02,630
to convey your message to him.

439
00:26:03,180 --> 00:26:04,660
What time is your bus departing?

440
00:26:05,380 --> 00:26:06,470
After 11.

441
00:26:42,630 --> 00:26:43,780
(The door is open)

442
00:27:00,750 --> 00:27:01,710
Why did you come back?

443
00:27:04,870 --> 00:27:05,630
Dad,

444
00:27:05,630 --> 00:27:07,660
I can't bear to leave you.

445
00:27:43,990 --> 00:27:44,710
Don't cry.

446
00:28:02,420 --> 00:28:03,500
There, there. Stop crying.

447
00:28:09,540 --> 00:28:10,300
That's enough.

448
00:28:10,710 --> 00:28:12,350
Grandpa and your mom are watching you.

449
00:28:13,470 --> 00:28:14,950
Don't make me lose face, okay?

450
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:16,870
Didn't we talk about this?

451
00:28:21,470 --> 00:28:22,140
That's enough.

452
00:28:23,140 --> 00:28:25,950
Dad, I can't bear to leave you.

453
00:28:26,630 --> 00:28:27,420
I know.

454
00:28:27,710 --> 00:28:28,830
I'll call you, okay?

455
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:31,070
That's enough.

456
00:28:36,470 --> 00:28:37,140
Okay.

457
00:28:40,380 --> 00:28:41,590
Remember to go for checkups on time.

458
00:28:42,070 --> 00:28:42,830
If anything happens,

459
00:28:42,830 --> 00:28:43,870
call me anytime.

460
00:28:44,380 --> 00:28:45,180
Okay.

461
00:28:45,420 --> 00:28:46,070
All right.

462
00:28:47,470 --> 00:28:48,540
Your mom is waiting.

463
00:28:48,990 --> 00:28:51,870
Dad, I don't want to leave you.

464
00:28:52,950 --> 00:28:54,230
Didn't we agree

465
00:28:56,500 --> 00:28:57,870
that a real man

466
00:28:57,870 --> 00:28:58,950
doesn't weep and sob?

467
00:29:00,750 --> 00:29:01,470
There, there.

468
00:29:07,870 --> 00:29:09,630
We'll come back when we're free,

469
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:14,780
Come on.

470
00:29:36,660 --> 00:29:37,540
Dr. Ning,

471
00:29:38,990 --> 00:29:39,990
thank you.

472
00:29:52,470 --> 00:29:53,110
Thank you so much.

473
00:29:54,780 --> 00:29:55,420
Let's go.

474
00:30:08,230 --> 00:30:08,870
Watch your head.

475
00:31:11,340 --> 00:31:13,660
(During the operation)

476
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:25,140
(When you're lying on
the operating table,)

477
00:31:25,230 --> 00:31:25,900
(it's equivalent)

478
00:31:25,900 --> 00:31:26,990
(to putting your life
in the doctor's hands.)

479
00:31:26,990 --> 00:31:27,630
(Do you know that?)

480
00:31:27,630 --> 00:31:28,750
(That's why I want to choose)

481
00:31:28,750 --> 00:31:29,750
(someone I can trust.)

482
00:31:38,380 --> 00:31:39,470
Verify the patient's identity.

483
00:31:39,830 --> 00:31:40,990
The patient's name is Ou Xiaoming.

484
00:31:40,990 --> 00:31:42,420
Male, age 26.

485
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:44,660
His hospital admission number
is 0308226.

486
00:31:46,500 --> 00:31:47,710
What are his vital signs?

487
00:31:49,110 --> 00:31:49,900
The indicators are normal.

488
00:31:51,350 --> 00:31:52,140
Let's start operating.

489
00:31:55,830 --> 00:31:56,590
Scalpel.

