00:32:38,380 --> 00:32:39,230
Rongeur.

493
00:32:41,780 --> 00:32:42,540
Gauze.

494
00:32:59,950 --> 00:33:00,870
How are his vital signs doing?

495
00:33:02,110 --> 00:33:03,020
The indicators are normal.

496
00:33:23,180 --> 00:33:23,950
Bipolar.

497
00:33:39,630 --> 00:33:40,350
Detacher.

