00:34:14,670 --> 00:34:15,590
Prepare the tray.

500
00:34:34,540 --> 00:34:35,430
Prepare to close him up.

501
00:34:36,700 --> 00:34:37,460
Thread.

502
00:34:38,020 --> 00:34:38,700
Forceps.

503
00:35:04,390 --> 00:35:05,070
Dr. Ruan,

504
00:35:05,590 --> 00:35:06,590
victory.

505
00:35:15,900 --> 00:35:18,660
(Beiya Hospital)

506
00:35:20,670 --> 00:35:21,500
When she comes in,

507
00:35:21,500 --> 00:35:22,670
you guys better be smart.

508
00:35:22,670 --> 00:35:23,070
Okay.

509
00:35:23,300 --> 00:35:23,740
Nice.

510
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:26,700
Well done.

511
00:35:26,780 --> 00:35:27,980
Thank you.

512
00:35:28,430 --> 00:35:29,350
You bought flowers?

513
00:35:29,350 --> 00:35:30,500
I paid for this myself.

514
00:35:32,430 --> 00:35:33,220
Dr. Ruan, congratulations

515
00:35:33,220 --> 00:35:34,780
on your first successful surgery
as the chief surgeon!

516
00:35:36,300 --> 00:35:36,910
Awesome.

517
00:35:37,700 --> 00:35:38,300
You were great.

518
00:35:38,780 --> 00:35:39,740
Ruan Liuzheng,

519
00:35:40,540 --> 00:35:42,110
I may not want to admit it.

520
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:44,430
But your performance was quite good

521
00:35:44,910 --> 00:35:45,780
just now.

522
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:47,830
Don't be humble

523
00:35:48,020 --> 00:35:48,940
or arrogant.

524
00:35:49,590 --> 00:35:50,500
Thank you.

525
00:35:50,500 --> 00:35:51,390
Ning,

526
00:35:51,700 --> 00:35:53,150
why aren't you complimenting
your student?

527
00:35:53,150 --> 00:35:54,870
Her skills are almost
as good as mine now.

528
00:36:02,020 --> 00:36:03,150
Hey, I'm talking to you.

529
00:36:05,430 --> 00:36:06,070
Look

530
00:36:06,260 --> 00:36:07,110
at his concentration.

531
00:36:07,110 --> 00:36:08,590
As expected
from the top neurosurgeon here.

532
00:36:13,700 --> 00:36:14,630
Mr. Ning

533
00:36:14,870 --> 00:36:15,980
wants some water.

534
00:36:16,740 --> 00:36:17,350
I'll do it.

535
00:36:20,110 --> 00:36:20,740
So

536
00:36:21,150 --> 00:36:21,670
everyone can leave now.

537
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:28,020
Don't pour it for him.

538
00:36:29,500 --> 00:36:30,260
Give him hot water

539
00:36:30,540 --> 00:36:30,940
and burn him.

540
00:36:31,190 --> 00:36:31,780
I'll get going now.

541
00:36:31,780 --> 00:36:32,220
Okay.

542
00:36:44,740 --> 00:36:45,540
Thanks.

543
00:37:12,700 --> 00:37:13,260
Hello?

544
00:37:13,630 --> 00:37:14,350
Yes, Mr. Ning.

545
00:37:15,110 --> 00:37:16,870
Is something wrong with Ou Xiaoming?

546
00:37:16,940 --> 00:37:17,630
No.

547
00:37:18,940 --> 00:37:19,870
Then...

548
00:37:20,590 --> 00:37:21,220
I know

549
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:22,460
you were waiting for me to call.

550
00:37:23,070 --> 00:37:23,670
Yes.

551
00:37:23,780 --> 00:37:24,980
I was waiting for your call.

552
00:37:25,740 --> 00:37:26,940
I just want to know

553
00:37:27,220 --> 00:37:28,740
what you think
about the surgery I performed.

554
00:37:29,910 --> 00:37:31,700
There may be some imperfections.

555
00:37:32,260 --> 00:37:33,590
But I want you to tell me

556
00:37:33,590 --> 00:37:35,150
which part I didn't do well.

557
00:37:35,430 --> 00:37:36,540
So I can fix it.

558
00:37:37,430 --> 00:37:38,260
The surgery was perfect.

559
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:39,670
I can't find any flaws.

560
00:37:40,590 --> 00:37:41,780
Then why didn't you say anything?

561
00:37:42,260 --> 00:37:42,870
I know

562
00:37:43,150 --> 00:37:44,190
you were waiting for me
to compliment you.

563
00:37:44,500 --> 00:37:45,500
But I won't do it.

564
00:37:45,910 --> 00:37:47,780
I'm not asking for compliments.

565
00:37:47,780 --> 00:37:49,110
I only want you

566
00:37:49,590 --> 00:37:50,630
to comment

567
00:37:50,780 --> 00:37:51,940
if I did well

568
00:37:51,940 --> 00:37:52,980
in the surgery.

569
00:37:53,300 --> 00:37:54,150
Why are you afraid

570
00:37:54,150 --> 00:37:55,070
that you're not good enough?

571
00:37:55,350 --> 00:37:56,350
You mustn't allow yourself

572
00:37:56,350 --> 00:37:57,220
to perform badly.

573
00:37:57,590 --> 00:37:58,670
Every surgery you perform

574
00:37:58,670 --> 00:37:59,940
must be perfect

575
00:38:00,220 --> 00:38:01,830
because every imperfection you do

576
00:38:01,980 --> 00:38:03,780
will affect the patient.

577
00:38:05,430 --> 00:38:06,190
Dr. Ruan,

578
00:38:06,700 --> 00:38:07,540
remember this.

579
00:38:07,980 --> 00:38:08,630
Perfection

580
00:38:08,870 --> 00:38:10,300
is not worthy of compliments

581
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:11,780
or something to be proud of.

582
00:38:13,020 --> 00:38:13,910
Because perfection

583
00:38:13,910 --> 00:38:15,830
is the basic requirement for a surgeon.

584
00:38:20,940 --> 00:38:21,740
Dr. Ruan?

585
00:38:22,630 --> 00:38:23,430
I'm still here.

586
00:38:24,020 --> 00:38:25,020
Did you keep quiet

587
00:38:25,630 --> 00:38:26,670
because you thought

588
00:38:26,670 --> 00:38:27,940
I was being too harsh?

589
00:38:29,070 --> 00:38:29,740
Not at all.

