00:38:32,070 --> 00:38:33,150
Where are you going tonight?

591
00:38:34,910 --> 00:38:35,630
Hey, Liuzheng.

592
00:38:35,910 --> 00:38:36,830
Mr. Xue?

593
00:38:36,940 --> 00:38:37,940
What are you doing here?

594
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:40,780
I'll hang up first.

595
00:38:42,190 --> 00:38:43,150
Your dad said

596
00:38:43,350 --> 00:38:44,260
you led surgery today.

597
00:38:45,460 --> 00:38:47,260
It looks like the surgery was a success.

598
00:38:50,350 --> 00:38:51,980
Congratulations
to our young and beautiful Dr. Ruan

599
00:38:51,980 --> 00:38:53,190
for the successful surgery.

600
00:38:53,190 --> 00:38:53,980
Thank you.

601
00:38:54,540 --> 00:38:55,390
This gift is too expensive.

602
00:38:55,390 --> 00:38:56,190
I can't accept this.

603
00:38:56,190 --> 00:38:57,190
Are doctors not allowed

604
00:38:57,190 --> 00:38:58,220
to accept gifts at the hospital?

605
00:38:58,430 --> 00:38:59,910
I'm not your patient.

606
00:39:01,350 --> 00:39:02,540
I think we could at least find a place

607
00:39:02,540 --> 00:39:03,390
to celebrate, right?

608
00:39:04,390 --> 00:39:05,590
Sure, let's go.

609
00:39:20,540 --> 00:39:21,150
This way.

610
00:39:40,740 --> 00:39:41,500
Hello.

611
00:39:42,110 --> 00:39:43,500
Are you Mr. Ning?

612
00:39:43,940 --> 00:39:45,780
You made a reservation
at our restaurant.

613
00:39:46,190 --> 00:39:47,430
So I'm calling to confirm

614
00:39:47,630 --> 00:39:48,500
your reservation for tonight.

615
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:51,190
I'm sorry.

616
00:39:51,460 --> 00:39:52,150
Can you cancel

617
00:39:52,150 --> 00:39:53,190
the reservation for me?

618
00:39:53,780 --> 00:39:54,460
Thank you.

619
00:40:07,190 --> 00:40:08,220
You're so lucky.

620
00:40:08,220 --> 00:40:09,500
This table was originally reserved
in advance.

621
00:40:09,500 --> 00:40:10,780
But they canceled at the last minute.
(Reserved)

622
00:40:11,500 --> 00:40:11,740
Have a seat.

623
00:40:11,740 --> 00:40:12,350
Thank you.

624
00:40:14,350 --> 00:40:15,110
Liuzheng,

625
00:40:15,500 --> 00:40:16,500
the place was fully booked

626
00:40:16,830 --> 00:40:17,500
when I called
to make a reservation this afternoon.

627
00:40:18,110 --> 00:40:19,110
But you insist on coming.

628
00:40:19,300 --> 00:40:20,700
It looks like you can't stop luck

629
00:40:20,700 --> 00:40:21,700
from coming.

630
00:40:22,870 --> 00:40:24,020
What would you like to order?

631
00:40:24,940 --> 00:40:27,110
A filet mignon steak, medium rare.

632
00:40:27,350 --> 00:40:28,260
And one

633
00:40:28,260 --> 00:40:29,390
tuna salad.

634
00:40:30,070 --> 00:40:30,870
You always come here?

635
00:40:31,460 --> 00:40:32,780
It's near to the hospital.

636
00:40:35,020 --> 00:40:35,910
I'll have

637
00:40:36,190 --> 00:40:37,780
a sirloin steak, medium rare.

638
00:40:37,780 --> 00:40:38,670
And a potato salad.

639
00:40:39,110 --> 00:40:40,260
