651
00:41:33,300 --> 00:41:34,460
I just remembered

652
00:41:35,390 --> 00:41:36,460
I have many precious memories

653
00:41:36,460 --> 00:41:37,670
in this restaurant.

654
00:41:38,150 --> 00:41:38,830
That's great.

655
00:41:39,630 --> 00:41:40,630
In the future, you'll also remember

656
00:41:40,940 --> 00:41:42,540
celebrating your first success

657
00:41:42,540 --> 00:41:44,190
as a chief surgeon with me here.

658
00:41:45,830 --> 00:41:47,110
Here's to you, Dr. Ruan.

659
00:41:47,110 --> 00:41:48,590
Congratulations on your first success
as the chief surgeon.

660
00:41:48,870 --> 00:41:49,540
Thank you.

